        <section class="- topic/section " id="section_uft_cph_1db" xtrc="section:1;8:22" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita"><title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:2;8:29" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">最大载重</title><indexterm class="- topic/indexterm " xtrc="indexterm:1;8:52" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">最大载重<index-sort-as class="+ topic/index-base indexing-d/index-sort-as " xtrc="index-sort-as:1;8:71" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">Z最大载重</index-sort-as></indexterm><p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;8:107" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">本系统检查床最大承重为
                250 kg，请勿将超过此重量的负载置于检查床之上。体重较大患者在检查床上集中施力会导致检查床装置损坏，或致使碳纤维床板与机架碰撞。</p><note class="- topic/note " type="caution" xtrc="note:1;10:32" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;11:20" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">人身伤害，系统损坏</p>
                <ul class="- topic/ul " id="ul_mdx_kdq_bdb" xtrc="ul:1;12:41" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:1;13:25" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:3;14:28" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">检查床承重过大有可能造成人身伤害或系统损坏。</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:2;16:25" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:4;17:28" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">请勿将超过 250 kg 的负载置于检查床上，这或将导致检查床故障或患者跌落。</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </note></section>
        <section class="- topic/section " id="section_whz_3ph_1db" xtrc="section:2;22:22" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita"><title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:3;22:29" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">危险位置</title><indexterm class="- topic/indexterm " xtrc="indexterm:2;22:52" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">危险位置<index-sort-as class="+ topic/index-base indexing-d/index-sort-as " xtrc="index-sort-as:2;22:71" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">W危险位置</index-sort-as></indexterm><p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:5;22:107" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">检查床移动时存在安全风险，可能造成人体损伤的危险位置上标识有如下标签。请勿将手或脚搁在以下位置，以防发生夹手、夹脚、身体挤压或其它人身危险。</p><image class="- topic/image " href="../../images/figure2-38.png" id="image_lyl_sdq_bdb" placement="inline" xtrc="image:1;23:95" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita"/><image class="- topic/image " href="../../images/figure2-11.png" id="image_rk1_tdq_bdb" placement="inline" xtrc="image:2;24:95" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita"/><image class="- topic/image " href="../../images/figure2-9.png" id="image_arm_tdq_bdb" placement="inline" xtrc="image:3;25:94" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita"/><note class="- topic/note " type="caution" xtrc="note:2;26:32" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:6;27:20" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">人身伤害</p>
                <ul class="- topic/ul " id="ul_qv3_12q_bdb" xtrc="ul:2;28:41" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:3;29:25" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:7;30:28" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">检查床和机架移动之前，请确认患者的四肢没有放到检查床侧盖或机架和检查床缝隙 之间。</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:4;32:25" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:8;33:28" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">操作前请仔细检查，以确保患者和其它设备之间不会出现干扰或碰撞。</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:5;35:25" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:9;36:28" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">在设备活动范围内不要放置无关物品。</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:6;38:25" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:10;39:28" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">无论患者还是操作人员，都不要在设备活动范围内停留，以免发生碰撞。</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:7;41:25" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:11;42:28" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">在进行患者定位前，请确保检查床的床板处于锁定状态。</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </note><fig class="- topic/fig " id="fig_xnj_rgq_bdb" xtrc="fig:1;45:46" xtrf="file:/D:/UIM项目/012%20Data/LianYing/data/General/系统操作手册/Topics/Safety/Patient_safety_before_the_scanning.dita">
